<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11361</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18399</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>星期一的早上，贝柔老师班的同学们都在说凯蒂的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但下一秒钟我就发现，她正从空中往下掉呢！” 乔伊跟同学们说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她尖叫了吗？” 劳拉问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊看了看奥利维亚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不记得了。她尖叫了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有。” 奥利维亚说，“她甚至都没哭。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40508</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爸爸抱起了她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40509</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44595</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈开车送他们去了医院。” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44596</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她的腿骨折了吗？” 拉里问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有，不过扭伤了脚踝。” 乔伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56677</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她几乎从脚趾到膝盖都缠满了绷带。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56678</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58839</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她得冰敷脚踝。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58840</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62800</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她至少两天不用来上学。” 奥利维亚说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看了看贝柔老师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69562</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是说她不能上学，她得休息。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69563</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77342</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“昨天你们的核桃把手推车装满了吗？” 贝柔老师问乔伊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77343</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79215</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，装满了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79216</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，爸爸和我把它们拿到了核桃收购站。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83020</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们得在价格下降以前拿过去！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊告诉大家核桃的价格会从15美分降到13美分。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92672</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98694</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我刚算好我的金钱目标，核桃价格就变了。” 乔伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98695</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真是太不公平了。” 她叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“ 核桃收购站的雷斯叔叔......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是我爸爸。” 卡洛斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊继续说道：“雷斯叔叔说价格下降是因为今年核桃太多了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，我还是不明白。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123395</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来解释一下。” 贝柔老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看，就像卡洛斯爸爸说的那样，今年的核桃非常多。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因此，核桃公司就会收购到足够的核桃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137708</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，核桃多得超过了人们的需求。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137709</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146171</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>包括车、房子，任何东西只要供大于求，就会导致价格下降。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148433</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊想了一会儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153731</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“核桃数量很少的时候，收购价格会高一些吗？” 她问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153732</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156515</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。” 贝柔老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156516</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161095</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为收购价格高，所以人们会更努力的捡核桃。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的目标快实现了吗？” 拉里问乔伊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊打开她的小本子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172137</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“星期六，我挣了25.5美元。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172138</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>星期天，我挣了24.45美元。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“乔伊要实现100美元的目标的话，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还需要再挣多少钱呢？” 贝柔老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190705</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>同学们开始计算起来。“多少钱，卢克？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190706</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194515</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“50.5美元。” 卢克回答说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194516</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197500</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“非常正确。” 乔伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203963</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就是说，我得再捡385磅核桃，才能修理小提琴。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203964</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天放学后，奥利维亚去看了凯蒂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212210</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她面朝着凯蒂，坐在乔伊的床上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212211</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215532</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看见我的绷带了吗？” 凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219523</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有我的冰袋！我得一直抬着这条腿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219524</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223140</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，我得把腿放在这个枕头上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223141</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“疼吗？” 奥利维亚问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有一点儿。” 凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233819</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不过，最糟糕的是我不能再帮乔伊了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233820</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那 ‘坐干草车’ 的活动怎么办呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利维亚说，“你能去吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“坐干草车！” 凯蒂用手拍了一下额头，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244508</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246610</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我差点儿忘了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246611</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249615</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你能帮我把桌子上的日历拿来吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249616</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251775</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天星期几？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251776</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“星期一。” 奥利维亚说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255129</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259478</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我必须在两周内好起来！” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259479</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263339</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她想了一会儿，然后叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263340</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“乔伊只有一个周末的时间可以捡核桃了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270440</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而且，她现在没有帮手了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270441</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊的小提琴在书桌上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276831</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利维亚摸了摸坏了的琴弦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276832</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279566</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她看了看凯蒂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279567</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有一个主意。” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284499</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以帮她！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284500</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>星期六早上，我会过来帮乔伊捡核桃的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>